Lolita refers to a brand of children's toys from [[fail|Woolworths]] ([http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/8521403.stm proof]).

Lolita may, [[shit nobody cares about|''rarely'']] refer to an [[allegedly]] fictional book about a [[pedophile|man]] and his relationship with a young girl who [[lie|made the first move in a sexual situation]]. However as this is [[moar]] [[lies|interesting]] this is what this article is about.

In the book, a [[pedophile]] marries an [[ugly]] woman so he can [[rape]] her daughter; however, before he does so the wife dies by [[murder|accident]]. The [[pedophile]] proceeds to [[stick it in her pooper]] while doing [[do a barrel roll|barrel rolls.]] Sadly for him, Chris Hansen asks him to [[chris hansen|take a seat over there]] and while he is sitting another pedophile steals the loli. Though he feels almost as though he had [[an hero|lost his ipod]], he manages eventually to find and [[pwn|kill]] the other pedo. Shame the girl's by now legal.

Until this book was published, Lolita was a popular name for girls. NO LONGER. And [[Gray area|nobody]] [[Shit nobody cares about|knows]] [[A bit sus|what]] [[Murder|happened]] to the Lolitas that were around when this book was published.

Lolita also refers to any young girl who wants [[sex|it]], and is the root word for [[loli]] and [[lolicon]].

[[CP|Teen modelling sites]] often draw upon Lolita for inspiration.

